OL,3,C'Reckless' BMW driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist
OL,6,FA "reckless" BMW driver who killed a
OL,7,Fcyclist while driving almost double
OL,8,Fthe speed limit has been jailed.
OL,10,FMariusz Zak was riding his bike along
OL,11,FHall Road in when a car driven by
OL,12,FAaron Metcalfe hit him on 18 December
OL,13,F2021.
OL,15,FThe 42-year-old father-of-two died in
OL,16,Fhospital a short time later.
OL,18,FMetcalfe, 35, had been driving at
OL,19,F54mph in a 30mph zone at the time.
