OL,3,C'Reckless' BMW driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist
OL,6,FHe was arrested and charged with
OL,7,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,8,Flater pleading guilty at Hull Crown
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FMichele Stuart-Lofthouse, prosecuting,
OL,12,Fsaid Metcalfe had a friend with him
OL,13,Fand was "showing off" about his new
OL,14,Fcar's performance when he collided
OL,15,Fwith Mr Zak.
OL,17,F"The speed of the BMW was such that
OL,18,Fthe defendant could not stop," Miss
OL,19,FStuart-Lofthouse said. Mr Zak died
OL,20,Ffrom head injuries.
