OL,3,C'Reckless' BMW driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist
OL,6,FMr Zak's widow, Justyna, said in a
OL,7,Fstatement given in court that her life
OL,8,Fhad "changed by 180 degrees" after he
OL,9,Fdied.JShe said: "He was almost half of
OL,10,Fmy life. One day changed everything
OL,11,Fand I was left alone. Since that day,
OL,12,FI have had to take care of everything
OL,13,Fby myself. I have to take care of our
OL,14,Fchildren. I need to be a mother and a
OL,15,Ffather at the same time, which is not
OL,16,Fan easy task."JShe added: "I lost my
OL,17,Fhusband, best friend, the person I
OL,18,Fcould speak to about everything."
OL,20,FMetcalfe was jailed for four years and
OL,21,Fbanned from driving for four years.
