OL,3,C'Reckless' BMW driver jailed after
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist
OL,6,FSgt Sean Hutchinson said: "The
OL,7,Freckless speeds that Metcalfe was
OL,8,Fdriving that night cost Mariusz his
OL,9,Flife, leaving his wife and two sons
OL,10,Fwith the unimaginable pain of
OL,11,Fnavigating a future without him.
OL,13,F"Whilst I know the outcome at court
OL,14,Fcan't change the horrific ordeal they
OL,15,Fhave experienced; I hope that it will
OL,16,Fbring them some comfort knowing that
OL,17,FMetcalfe his now being punished for
OL,18,Fhis actions."
